{"tid":692784,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[食死貓] 港鐵:分判商泛迅工人剪短鋼筋","createTime":"2018-06-07T03:13:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-07T03:46:15.000Z","uid":77196,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"ab5dff4f2964d421c5b7eb6116ac5db52cd3f0fa","tid":692784,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T03:13:32.000Z","msg":"港鐵(00066)沙中線紅磡站擴建工程鋼筋被剪短事件，工程總監黃唯銘今早在一個電台節目表示，根據監督人員的滙報，<span style=\"color: red;\">是分判商泛迅的工人剪短鋼筋</span>。<br />\n<br />\n黃唯銘指出，在5次巡查中只有1次文件紀錄，是因為在2015年12月巡查期間，發現有5支鋼筋被剪短，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>巡查人員感到很憤怒，向大判「禮頓」發警告信，禮頓亦向泛迅發警告信，但沒有量度被剪短多少</strong></span>。至於其餘4次巡查，每次均發現少於4支鋼筋被剪短，由於巡查人員已經即時要求工人糾正，將有問題鋼筋換走，因此沒有紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵行政總裁梁國權指出，根據監督人員的滙報，以及文字記錄資料，推算有問題的鋼筋總數少於20多支。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵主席馬時亨則表示，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>會就事件作全面檢討，回頭想如果遇到同一情況，應該向董事局下的工程小組滙報，可以增強公眾對工程的信心</strong></span>。他認為，承建商禮頓應該開誠布公向公眾交代事件，確保2.6萬粒螺絲帽無問題，是法例上對承建商的要求。"},{"pid":"e80dd3c87c917943b02b8025fa180d4d978202f6","tid":692784,"uid":82175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T03:16:36.000Z","msg":"憤怒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"035598f8b965dfb526cda34ee12028fe695848d5","tid":692784,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T03:18:53.000Z","msg":"好有戲劇feel"},{"pid":"cae8d873fdf1c1db38e002082363a9ff747f0a65","tid":692784,"uid":78016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e80dd3c87c917943b02b8025fa180d4d978202f6","tid":692784,"uid":82175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T03:16:36.000Z","msg":"憤怒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T03:21:41.000Z","msg":"成件事加入個人情感錯曬<br />\n如果個iow 唔覺得憤怒就無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔係因為不符合規格 而係因為iow 個人情感重做"},{"pid":"b1c69c4348a37163aa1cefc1d3f1c43c35c76513","tid":692784,"uid":179467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T03:22:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>他認為，承建商禮頓應該開誠布公向公眾交代事件，確保2.6萬粒螺絲帽無問題，是法例上對承建商的要求。</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e524819950dc9e3eac7055be28d20dbf4a23f65a","tid":692784,"uid":18251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T03:25:03.000Z","msg":"終於作完個古仔。"},{"pid":"f0e3224055b09d9d457942265d85de0be4dd076f","tid":692784,"uid":168172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T03:25:54.000Z","msg":"又係外判硬食<br />\n<br />\n做狗都唔好做外判"},{"pid":"fe0522ec1d696c4d20bcb18c54f74b45dbdbdb33","tid":692784,"uid":68094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T03:36:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8481291f1f8863e82a33feafa40f587924afea22","tid":692784,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T03:37:16.000Z","msg":"鉛水都係屈個水喉佬"},{"pid":"21828265b0aaa0d3c2a8967c070da0b6907d5fbe","tid":692784,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T03:38:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 賴鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"307310f21cbdbc882acfbabeb3e12272872ccc96","tid":692784,"uid":137627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T03:42:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">黃唯銘指出，在5次巡查中只有1次文件紀錄，是因為在2015年12月巡查期間，發現有5支鋼筋被剪短，巡查人員感到<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">很憤怒</span></span></strong></span><br />\n講得出唔覺柒先好野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44ed94f28d6dee053031d921f634c452e0683273","tid":692784,"uid":33456,"like":0,"disl